        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the skin from the <strong>smoked mackerel fillets</strong></p>\n<p>Tear the <strong>mackerel</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>\n<p>Add the<strong> torn mackerel</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>cornflour</strong> and give it a gentle mix up until the mackerel is fully coated</p>",
